Tonea Stewart https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tonea_Stewart 0 Tonea Stewart (born February 3, 1947), also Tommie Stewart, is an American actress and university professor. She is dean of the College of Visual and Performing Arts of Alabama State University in Montgomery, Alabama. She had a recurring role as Aunt Etta Kibbe in the American television series In the Heat of the Night.
